{"tid":896983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周浩鼎：東涌「水浸眼眉」 倡准旅巴載散客至各區","createTime":"2018-11-10T13:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T19:08:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae47e10b742539499979a45d57745cf68f64f0e","tid":896983,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋開通後，導致大批內地旅客聚集在東涌大排長龍等候過境巴士，旅客迫爆，令區內居民不堪其擾。民建聯立法會議員、離島區議員周浩鼎建議政府特事特辦，容許旅遊巴在口岸接載旅行團以外的散客到各區。<br />\n      <br />\n      周浩鼎出席一電台節目時形容，東涌情況是「水浸眼眉」，非常嚴重，他希望當局搬遷東涌B6巴士站至遠離民居的地方，以及當人流多的時政府可特事特辦，容許旅遊巴到香港口岸接，接載旅行團以外的個人遊旅客到各區不同景點，以達到分流作用。<br />\n      <br />\n      周浩鼎又指， 留意到部分沒有香港旅行社接待的內地團，試圖走法律罅，促請當局加強巡查和「放蛇」拘捕未持本港導遊證的內地領隊。<br />\n      <br />\n      香港入境團旅行社協會創會會長謝淦廷表示，非法旅行團是「走法律隙」，香港無法管理，他希望香港成立旅遊局做好旅遊配套。他認為，長遠而言，本港旅行社未來需與內地旅行社合作推出更多香港景點遊路線，以分流經港珠澳大橋入境的內地旅客。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=250747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D250747&d=oMbJSBbaPIxa%2BWjmUQq06Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=646249e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D250747&h=a8eae31b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=250747</a>"},{"pid":"ff51b5f778858653d12a2036b803e2444eecb8af","tid":896983,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/photo/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_04b.jpg?20181110190027\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20181110190027&h=d497d43d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba7e66eb22da5bb73039ae68ae810fd360734cb","tid":896983,"uid":17510,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"真。光復大行動<br />\n<br />\n要趕走周浩鼎 就要組團入東涌撐支那蝗<br />\n將矛頭指向民建聯<br />\n再加多幾句話 要不是支那，東涌人飯都無得開<br />\n<br />\n唯有咁樣先可以引起東涌居民反彈<br />\n趕走民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n區議員話要限制遊客？我地要反其道而行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯有趕走周浩鼎先至係真真正正咁光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff3f2ecb3eb4416cb91b97700cd513153f8636a","tid":896983,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"各區居民：%&yen;※@＆%#@！！※"},{"pid":"9e64fe74ca3eda206526266ac09242a82f7b85a6","tid":896983,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"其實plan 好哂將支那狗送去東涌，咁市區咁少d支那狗囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後再送上大橋，一步一步趕出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccf6cb373489e7a467dbbd91906839b3bd6f30f","tid":896983,"uid":217634,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f41c4d1bbf64856ac29efc97e6e63d9dfef65a04","tid":896983,"uid":217634,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24121f0acedb358dd7c8b0c2cc7c826fd380c8e7","tid":896983,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da05590379ff3b8927c9ff1896feb187dca2281","tid":896983,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"己所不欲，勿施於人呀。"},{"pid":"e5dcc2a31c91bdda518841f2099104da386408a6","tid":896983,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"刁民"},{"pid":"62a66d9fbdff23184fb0bdf71c91148cc6a882a3","tid":896983,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi